We have an exciting 12 month fixed term contract for a Accounts Receivable Accountant within Wolters Kluwer Health (WKH) Division, Clinical Effectiveness. This role reports into WKH Senior Finance Manager giving excellent International exposure.

This new role will support all International business outside US and Canada, and it would help improve the finance support function with quicker access to customers, and increased efficiency and customer satisfaction thanks to regional knowledge and experience. The Accounts Receivable Accountant will process daily cash receipts application to our customer accounts, issuing accounts statements and automated payments reminders to our clients, also be following up on overdue invoices.

Claire Morrow
